BT /F2 17 Tf 262.28 748.00 Td (Abstract) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 690.00 Td (The AI Recipe Generator is a web-based application designed to help users create) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 674.00 Td (recipes from available ingredients, dietary preferences, cuisine choices, cooking) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 658.00 Td (time, and serving requirements. The system reduces the everyday difficulty of deciding) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 642.00 Td (what to cook by combining a clean user interface with AI-assisted recipe generation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 616.00 Td (The application provides user authentication, profile management, pantry tracking,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 600.00 Td (recipe generation, saved recipes, shopping list support, meal planning, and preference) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 584.00 Td (management. The frontend is developed using React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, React Router,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 568.00 Td (Axios, and Lucide icons. The backend uses Node.js, Express.js, JWT authentication,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 552.00 Td (bcrypt password hashing, PostgreSQL, Sequelize, and the Google GenAI package for AI) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 536.00 Td (integration.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 510.00 Td (The project focuses on usability, personalization, data security, and practical meal) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 494.00 Td (planning. It supports a structured database design for users, preferences, pantry) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 478.00 Td (items, recipes, nutrition, meal plans, and shopping lists.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 452.00 Td (Keywords: AI, recipe generation, meal planning, pantry management, React, Express,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 436.00 Td (PostgreSQL, JWT.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 295.04 28.00 Td (v) Tj ET
endstream
