BT /F2 18 Tf 62.00 775.89 Td (1 About Project) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 747.89 Td (1.1 Title) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 726.89 Td (AI Recipe Generator) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 703.89 Td (1.2 Domain) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 682.89 Td (Artificial Intelligence, Food Technology, Web Application Development, Personal) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 666.89 Td (Productivity, and Meal Planning.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 643.89 Td (1.3 Aim) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 622.89 Td (The aim of this project is to develop a web application that generates useful recipes) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 606.89 Td (from user-provided ingredients and personal food preferences while also helping users) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 590.89 Td (manage pantry items, saved recipes, meal plans, and shopping lists.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 567.89 Td (1.4 Objective) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 546.89 Td (- Provide secure login, signup, and protected user pages.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 528.89 Td (- Allow users to enter ingredients or use pantry items for recipe generation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 510.89 Td (- Support cuisine type, dietary restriction, serving size, and cooking time) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 494.89 Td (preferences.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 476.89 Td (- Display generated recipes with ingredients, instructions, time, difficulty, tags,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 460.89 Td (and nutrition.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 442.89 Td (- Maintain database tables for users, preferences, recipes, pantry, meal plans, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 426.89 Td (shopping lists.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 403.89 Td (1.5 Problem Statement) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 382.89 Td (Many users struggle to decide what to cook with ingredients already available at home.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 366.89 Td (Existing recipe websites usually require manual searching and do not adapt well to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 350.89 Td (pantry stock, dietary restrictions, serving count, and preferred cuisines. This project) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 334.89 Td (solves the problem by generating personalized recipe suggestions and organizing the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 318.89 Td (cooking workflow in a single application.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 295.04 28.00 Td (1) Tj ET
