BT /F2 18 Tf 62.00 775.89 Td (2 Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 747.89 Td (2.1 Overview) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 726.89 Td (AI Recipe Generator is a full-stack web application. The React frontend provides pages) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 710.89 Td (for dashboard, pantry, recipe generator, saved recipes, recipe details, meal planner,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 694.89 Td (shopping list, login, signup, and settings. The backend is built using Express.js and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 678.89 Td (PostgreSQL, with JWT based authentication and user preference APIs.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 655.89 Td (2.2 Motivation) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 634.89 Td (Food waste and meal decision fatigue are common daily problems. A user may have) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 618.89 Td (ingredients available but may not know how to combine them into a complete dish. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 602.89 Td (motivation of this project is to make cooking decisions faster, more personal, and more) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 586.89 Td (organized.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 563.89 Td (2.3 Project Scope and Limitations) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 542.89 Td (- Scope includes user account management, recipe generation workflow, pantry) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 526.89 Td (tracking, meal planning, and shopping list support.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 508.89 Td (- The current frontend uses dummy recipe data for some screens while the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 492.89 Td (architecture is prepared for API integration.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 474.89 Td (- AI output quality depends on prompt design, available ingredients, and model) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 458.89 Td (response quality.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 440.89 Td (- Internet access and API keys are required for production AI generation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 417.89 Td (2.4 Methodology of Problem Solving) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 396.89 Td (The project follows an iterative development method. Requirements are identified from) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 380.89 Td (daily cooking workflows, modules are separated into frontend pages and backend services,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 364.89 Td (and data is stored in a relational database. Authentication and protected routes ensure) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 348.89 Td (that each user sees only personal data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 295.04 28.00 Td (2) Tj ET
endstream
