BT /F2 18 Tf 62.00 775.89 Td (3 Literature Survey) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 62.00 747.89 Td (3.1 Similar Work) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 726.89 Td (Recipe websites, meal planner applications, and pantry management tools already exist.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 710.89 Td (However, many systems focus on only one part of the process. Some provide static) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 694.89 Td (recipes, some provide grocery planning, and some provide diet tracking. This project) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 62.00 678.89 Td (combines these ideas with AI assisted recipe creation.) Tj ET
